children.name: Rules
children.text:
This weapon, while sporting a scythe blade, is treated as a quarterstaff. It is a +1 weapon that deals an extra 1d4 necrotic damage. It can also be used as a spell focus. 
If this weapon scores a critical hit, either with a melee attack or a spell attack, the wielder regains 1d4 spell slots if they are a Wizard, Sorcerer, Warlock, or Bard. Once this ability is used it cannot be used again until after a long rest.
